OL,5, Hollywood star Charlize Theron has     
OL,6, faced a mountain of criticism for      
OL,7, calling her mother tongue Afrikaans "a 
OL,8, dying language".                       
OL,10,FTheron joked it was spoken by "about 44
OL,11,Fpeople" and was "not very helpful".    
OL,13,FShe made the comments on the SmartLess 
OL,14,Fpodcast, saying she grew up in South   
OL,15,FAfrica speaking only Afrikaans before  
OL,16,Flearning English aged 19, which is why 
OL,17,Fshe speaks it with an American accent. 
OL,19,FSome of the millions in South Africa   
OL,20,Fwho do speak Afrikaans were not happy. 
